Research shows consuming 📈 linoleic acid (Omega-6s) can:

🫀

Increase harmful oxidation in the LDL cholesterol and blood plasma of atherosclerosis patients.

🧠

Induce obesity and diabetes, and alter the regulation of the brain’s hunger signaling in the hypothalamus.

🍼️

Reduce sperm count, quality and mobility, and testicular volume.

🦴

Promote inflammation and be found 2x higher in bones with osteoporosis.

💭

Result in significant deficits of working memory and synapse health.

🍟

Cause fatty tissue to accumulate, while reducing dietary PUFA reverses the obesogenic effect of a high-fat diet.

🥲

Lead to higher rates of mood disorders and depression in young people.
